Thanks for installing CtrlrX!

CtrlrX by Damien Sellier is an alternative fork of Ctrlr by Roman Kubiak under BSD|GPL license. The 'X' in CtrlrX represents a commitment to delivering extra features, extended functionalities, and a collaborative space for its evolution.

About the Original Ctrlr:

Ctrlr allows you to control any MIDI-enabled hardware: synthesizers, drum machines, samplers, effects. Create custom User Interfaces and host them as VST or AU plugins in your favorite DAWs.

For more info, visit https://github.com/damiensellier/CtrlrX

